      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the funding, everything. i'm sitting here looking at these debt notices and i just... i can't even think about going back home. how do i even look my parents in the eye after i blew everything they helped me build? it feels like there's no way to fix this. there is no coming back from this kind of shame.",
